com.inqwell.any.ref

Class AnyWeakReference

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.ref.Reference<T>
      • java.lang.ref.WeakReference<Any>
        • com.inqwell.any.ref.AnyWeakReference
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Any, Reference, WeakReference, Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AnyWeakListener

    public class AnyWeakReference
extends WeakReference<Any>
implements WeakReference
    Extends the standard JDK SoftReference class to make it a collectable Any and to form a base for other classes wishing to store extra data with the reference.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
